    <li> The colored-in state from Ryan's sketch because it provides context for the pie chart.
    </li>
    <li> A key for each of the diagrams.
    </li>
    <li> The buttons from Maia's sketch because they work as great signifiers.
    </li>
    <li> The paragraphs/titles from Maia's sketch because they make the page more understandable.
    </li>
  </ol>
